These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, american, thai
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, animation, crime
1. the pakistani is in an even position##4
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
3. the person watching action movies is the american##1
4. the thai is on the far left##1
5. the person watching animation movies is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Nationality   | thai | pakistani | american |
| Movie-Genre    | animation    | crime | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, scrabble
There 3 different types of food: lemon, pineapple, blueberry
1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person eating pineapple is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Game       | bridge | scrabble | canasta |
| Food   | blueberry    | pineapple     | lemon        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, bird, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting, sailing
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Pet         | turtle     | bird | frog |
| Sport   | weightlifting | biathlon     | sailing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different games are played: billiard, chess, mah-jongg
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, train
1. the person playing chess is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person playing billiard is the person driving the train##1
3. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Game   | mah-jongg | chess  | billiard  |
| Transport         | jet-ski  | roller | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, january
3 different games are played: poker, go, scrabble
1. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person playing poker##2
2. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Birthday         | april   | january | december    |
| Game   | go | scrabble     | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, classical
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the fan of rock is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | classical | rock   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, pilot, designer
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, bus
1. the pilot is on the right of the coach##1
2. the coach is between the person driving the bus and the designer##2
3. the coach is on the left of the pilot##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Job   | designer | coach | pilot |
| Transport           | jet-ski         | skateboard         | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, japanese, brazilian
House: wooden, modern, ranch-style
1. the wooden house is between the modern house and the mexican##2
2. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
3. the modern house is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Nationality   | japanese | brazilian | mexican |
| House    | modern    | wooden | ranch-style     |

