.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, potato, strawberry
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, rose
1. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person eating potato##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Food   | strawberry   | potato  | kiwi  |
| Flower         | rose | dahlia | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
City: marseilles, nizza, london
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, bartender, lawyer
1. the manager is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the lawyer is in an even position##4
3. the lawyer is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| City   | marseilles    | london      | nizza |
| Job       | bartender | lawyer | manager   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
City: venice, rome, hamburg
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| City         | rome | hamburg | venice |
| Game   | bridge | monopoly   | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
3 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, whist
House: cottage, palace, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the person playing domino is the farmhouse house##1
3. the palace house is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
4. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Game   | whist | mah-jongg | domino |
| House     | palace     | cottage   | farmhouse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, indie, d&b
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, spinach, pineapple
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person eating cucumber is the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | r&b | indie   |
| Food         | spinach | pineapple   | cucumber |

