.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, skiing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, milk
1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person drinking juice##2
2. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | swimming | skiing | water-polo |
| Beverage     | coffee    | milk  | juice   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
