3 different games are played: domino, go, mah-jongg
1. the engineer is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Job   | security-guard  | engineer     | librarian |
| Game   | go | domino | mah-jongg    |

