.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, egyptian, argentine
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, november, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the argentine##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the american##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Nationality          | argentine | american | egyptian  |
| Birthday   | june      | october  | november |

