3 different games are played: poker, monopoly, go
1. the person playing go is on the right of the polish##1
2. the polish is in the middle##1
3. the malaysian is the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing poker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality         | malaysian | polish   | british |
| Game   | monopoly   | poker | go      |

