.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
3 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, canasta
House: art-deco, cottage, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
2. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Game      | snooker | mah-jongg | canasta |
| House   | cottage   | cape-cod          | art-deco |

