.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, subway, tram
City: hamburg, edinburgh, london
1. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Transport     | subway  | tram   | train |
| City   | london | edinburgh | hamburg       |

 